                             'SunMaze' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'SunMaze' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to place mirrors,
so they reflect the sun's ray so it gets to an arrival position,
located somewhere in the labyrinth. To complicate matters a little,
only a small portion (a 5 by 5 space area) of the labyrinth is
shown...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

